        "last_activity_date": 1542965886,
        "creation_date": 1542965886,
        "body": "<blockquote>\n  <p>android.database.sqlite.SQLiteException: near \"Pertama\": syntax error\n  (code 1): , while compiling: INSERT INTO <code>Table1<\/code>\n  (name,address,phone,id) VALUES (WK,Taman Pertama,NULL,'4');<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p>Is saying that you have a syntax error. Strings/Text should be enclosed in single quotes.<\/p>\n\n<p>So need need to use something like<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>INSERT INTO Table1 (name,address,phone,id) VALUES ('WK','Taman Pertama',NULL,4);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>i.e. WK and Taman Pertama need to be enclosed in quotes the number doesn't need to be.<\/p>\n",
